riday, September 23rd.", Kytn</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>Pardon me for asking this - but why wont there be a set of&nbsp;answers this month?</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>By not answering a single question for more than <strong><u>5 weeks</u></strong> this entire things gets an air of stalling to it - rather than&nbsp;the&nbsp;fresh air&nbsp;from wanting to communicate with us I hope its meant to give.</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>So, I humbly ask that you put to your bosses that if this is meant as anything but a charade and&nbsp;I assume it is meant as more then answering questions should not wait 5 weeks. Rather it should happen soon&nbsp;&nbsp;- and without the use of the dreaded "just wait and see what we have in the coming expansion" kind of answers. Disclose some real info or dont bother, please.</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>I am looking forward to seeing what happens. My jaded side is screaming no hard questions will be answered in real detail or any time soon - but my optimistic side is trying to convince me you wouldnt try to pull a fast one on us. Before the 5 week part my optimistic side still had a chance - but now I fear my jaded side took a huge lead. Please put my jadeness to shame by getting us some honest straightforward answers to a good deal of the questions asked - much sooner than in 5 weeks from now.</div><p>Message Edited by Mikar on <span class="date_text">08-16-2005</span><span class="time_text">06:43 PM</span><br></p><hr></blockquote><div></div><p>Message Edited by Maebe on <span class=date_text>06-06-2006</span> <span class=time_text>10:41 AM</span>
				
